  &lt;p id="zz1fkU"&gt;The Pixel Tablet 2 may &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302508/google-pixel-tablet-2-canceled-rumor"&gt;never see the light of day&lt;/a&gt;, but new details &lt;a href="https://www.androidauthority.com/exclusive-canceled-pixel-tablet-2-3504100/"&gt;reported by &lt;em&gt;Android Authority&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; reveal what Google may have had up its sleeve for the sophomore device, including a high-refresh display, 5G connectivity, and more. &lt;/p&gt;
